source.en: Blaser, Magdalena "Myths of the Cofán people"

sentences.text: Tayopi tsu a'indeccuja atesu'fa ma'caen Chiga agattoemba antte'choma.
Chigata tsu agattoen sefacco, ande toya'caen ande tsosini jin'chove.
Puiyi'cco a'ingi injan'jenfa ma'caen Chigaja ti'tsse'tssiave.
Tsa cocoyandeccuja tise'ma paña'fambi.
Tise tsu ccaninga've cambian'su.
Toya'caen va andenijan cocoyandeccu tsu canse'fa.
Tayopi'su condase'cho tsu jin ma'caen na'en coemba pa'cco va ande'su canse'chondeccuma fi'tti'choma.
Tsaninda'te ccoanifae'cco a'iyi ccusha'fa.
Pa'ccote tssipaccuyi.
Tsanga Chigaja jipa ande onccan'choma iyofapae afe.
Tsa iyofaja andema amba ti'tsse'ccoe ccopa boña'su.
Tsa tsu tsa'caen tson'ñacca injan'tssi andeve atapoen.
Tsa'caen atapoensi shoshovi, quini'si tsa'ye sho'yo'fa.
Quini'si atapasi tse'ija osha'cho tsampini canseqque'su atapa'fa.
Tsa'caen atapapa tsu pa'cco andenga atapa'fa, cuintsu jai'ngae a'indeccuja tsama amba canse'faye.
Tsa'caen pa'cco va andenga osha'choja atapa'fa, cuintsu a'indeccuja amba opatsse canse'faye.
Sefacconi'qque tsu antte tseni'qque faesu ccaninga jin'choye.
Pa'cco sefacconi jinqque'su coe'je, o'fe, ofendyo'ndyo, an'cco, ataje'cho, coseje'cho toya'caen ccovu.
Coe'jeta tsu a'ta chanjun'jeñe, ccovu toya'caen o'feja cose chanjun'jen'faye.
Toya'caen tsu condase'fa coe'jeta te tsandie toya'caen ccovuta'te pushesu.
Ofeta te a'indeccu.
Tise'pa yayama fi'tti'fasi tteyayepa secconi japa canse'fa'chondeccu.
Tise'pa yayaja ande tsosini tsu cansenga.
Andeta tsu a'indeccu canse'cho toya'caen cocoyandeccu canse'cho.
Cocoyandeccuja iyicca'ye'ta tsu a'ima an'fa.
Toya'caen ttesi, canjansi, vasaga, nane osha'chove tsu dapa attian'jen'fa.
Tsa'camba tsu a'i pushesunga piye atesu'fa.
Tsa'caen pipa tsu a'i pushesunga du'sian'faya.
Cocoyandeccuja attia'ma'sia tsu, tsa'ma maquita tsu ñoa'me attian'faya.
Nane canjansi ta tsu osha'cho na'en'sumbe chan'can.
Tsa'caeñi tsu pa'cco tsampini canse'chondeccu'qque tise'pa nasundeccuma an'bian'fa.
Consindeccuja tise'pa iyoma, ttesi chiminde tsu tise'pa iyoma an'bian'fa.
Coragandeccu tsu osha'fa va cocoyandeccui'ccu condaseye'ja.
Tsa'camba tsu mundama ttu'se'fa, cuintsu jisi a'indecu fi'ttipa an'faye.
Toya'caen tsampini tsu canse'fa attiambi a'indeccuja.
Tsendeccumajan majan osha'chondeccuyi tsu atte'jeye osha'fa.
Tsa tsu pa'cco.
